<title>PHILIPPINES: Kuok Philippines to raise capital stock.</title>
<headline>Kuok Philippines to raise capital stock.</headline>
<dateline>MANILA 1997-06-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Kuok Philippine Properties Inc said on Monday its board approved an increase in authorised capital stock to 10 billion pesos from the present 3.9 billion.</p>
<p>Kuok corporate secretary Cynthia Laureta told the Philippine Stock Exchange the proposed capital hike will be submitted to the stockholders for approval on June 23.</p>
<p>The capital increase will consist of seven billion common shares and three billion preferred shares, both with a par value of one peso per share.</p>
